OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FA mine worker from Tredegar says the
OL,8,Fpension scheme boost for former
OL,9,Fmineworkers unveiled in Rachel Reeves'
OL,10,FBudget has "been a long time coming",
OL,11,Fbut the UK Government is giving with
OL,12,Fone hand and taking with the other.
OL,14,FIt comes after the UK Government
OL,15,Fannounced moves to overturn an
OL,16,F"historic injustice" involving the
OL,17,Fpensions of former mine workers.
