OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FMinisters said more than 100,000
OL,8,Fformer mineworkers will receive
OL,9,F#1.5billion of money kept from their
OL,10,Fpensions.
OL,12,F"We've been fighting for over 10 years
OL,13,Ffor this money of miners' pension,"
OL,14,Fretired miner Ken Sullivan told ITV
OL,15,FCymru Wales.
OL,17,F"It's been a long time coming as it's
OL,18,Fover the amount of money that the
OL,19,Fgovernment has robbed from the miners.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
