OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"But it's nice to have something come
OL,8,Fback to the miners from #1.2billion to
OL,9,F#1.5billion out of the investment of
OL,10,Fthe funds."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, universal winter fuel
OL,13,Fallowance has been scrapped and will
OL,14,Fonly be paid to those on pension
OL,15,Fcredit.
OL,17,FMr Sullivan added: "When you look at
OL,18,Fit in real terms, what they've given
OL,19,Fus in one hand, and they've robbed us
OL,20,Fof our winter allowance from the other
OL,21,Fhand.
