OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"So, we're not really gaining anything
OL,8,Fout of it at all. It's another form of
OL,9,Frobbery by the government that has
OL,10,Fbeen done to the miners over the past
OL,11,F25 years."
OL,13,FFollowing Wednesday's Budget, UK
OL,14,Fenergy secretary Ed Miliband confirmed
OL,15,Fthe move will mean a 32% increase to
OL,16,Fthe annual pensions of 112,000 former
OL,17,Fmineworkers, an average increase of
OL,18,F#29 per week for each member.
