OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FAn investment reserve fund set up
OL,8,Fusing profits from the Mineworkers'
OL,9,FPension Scheme in 1992, to provide a
OL,10,Fbuffer in case it went into deficit,
OL,11,Fwas due to be returned to government
OL,12,Fin 2029.
OL,14,FThe fund, now worth #1.5billion, will
OL,15,Fbe handed over to the pension scheme.
OL,17,FMr Miliband said: "We owe the mining
OL,18,Fcommunities who powered this country a
OL,19,Fdebt of gratitude.
