OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"For decades, it has been a scandal
OL,8,Fthat the government has taken money
OL,9,Fthat could have been passed to the
OL,10,Fminers and their families.
OL,12,F"Today, that scandal ends, and the
OL,13,Fmoney is rightfully transferred to the
OL,14,Fminers.
OL,16,F"I pay tribute to the campaigners who
OL,17,Fhave fought for justice, today is
OL,18,Ftheir victory."
