OL,3,C'It's been a long time coming' ` Ex-
OL,4,Cmine worker welcomes Budget pension
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FMinister for industry Sarah Jones
OL,8,Fsaid: "Miners powered our industries
OL,9,Fand our homes for decades.
OL,11,F"That's why we have to right the wrong
OL,12,Fthat has denied them the decent
OL,13,Fpension they deserved.
OL,15,F"We are handing over the #1.5billion
OL,16,Fthat for years has sat in the reserve
OL,17,Ffund unused at times when people
OL,18,Fneeded it most.
