OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"This will end an historic injustice
OL,8,Fand will ensure members of the scheme
OL,9,Fsee an average increase of #29 per
OL,10,Fweek added to their pay, an increase
OL,11,Fof 32%."
OL,13,FGary Saunders, chairman of the
OL,14,Ftrustees of the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,15,FScheme, said: "As a trustee board we
OL,16,Fare delighted we will be able to put
OL,17,Fmore money in our members' pockets.
